caller_intent: Ron inquired about insurance options in Florida, likely seeking coverage or services from Alliance Insurance Services.

She advised Ron to contact a local Florida-based agency for better assistance.
She provided her contact number for follow-up questions.

Insurance carrier partnerships in North Carolina vs. Florida
